@node what "WHAT IS ADDRESSMANAGER"
AddressManager is an utility which  makes it easier to you to  master all the
information you have  about your friends, familly, business partners or pets.
It is not a professional Databanking-System but it has a lot of advantages if
you just want to manage names, telephone numbers etc. of some people:
- AddressManager is very easy to use.You can learn all the functions in a few
  minutes.
- AddressManager needs WB 2.0 or higher, therefore:
  - it uses things like AppIcons and AppWindows
  - if you own WB 2.1 or higher you can use it in English or German language
  - it looks quite good
- AddressManager is @{"SHAREWARE" link share}.You can copy it, test it and if you like it you
  just send me a few money to get a registered user. Then you also can use
  the advantages of my special @{"SERVICE" link service}.
@endnode

